# AI Content Calendar + Auto-Scheduler

## Problem
Small D2C brands and coaching institutes need consistent social media presence.
Creating daily content manually is time-consuming and inconsistent.

## Solution
Google Sheet content calendar → ChatGPT/Gemini generates captions → Make.com schedules posts automatically.

## Tools Used
- Google Sheets (content calendar template)
- OpenAI / Gemini API (caption generation)
- Make.com (scheduling trigger)
- Buffer / native scheduling (post delivery)

## How It Works
1. Owner fills 3 columns in Sheet: Topic, Platform, Tone
2. Make.com triggers on new row
3. AI generates caption based on inputs
4. Caption written back to Sheet + scheduled for posting

## Output Example
Input: Topic = "New batch starting June", Platform = Instagram, Tone = Excited
Output: "June batch is HERE! 🚀 Limited seats — DMs open for enquiries. Your consistency starts now."

## Business Impact
- 7-day content planned in 20 minutes
- Zero daily content stress
- Consistent brand voice

